      class  Lightning
      Lightning is a subclass of Level, there is only a fixed amount of time for moves to be made.
      class  Puzzle
      Puzzle is a subclass of Level, win by removing at least all but two pieces from the bullpen before the move limit is reached.
      class  Release
      Release is a subclass of Level, win by freeing number sets.
